overview: First, Erik comes home to find Aaliyah resting on the couch. Erik tries not to wake her but fails. She then starts to hit on Erik, but he thinks she's too young. Aaliyah won't have any of that and throws herself at Erik. Next, Evilyn and Mr. tate (Evan Stone) are enjoying a glass of water on an extremely hot day. Mr. Tate watches Evilyn while she seductively rubs the glass all over her body, thats when things really heat up. Up next, Mr. B's (Billy Glide) old basketball injury comes back again so his wife gets Lyla to look after him. Lyla brings Mr. B to law down and then offers a back massage, things start to get heavy when Mr. B turns over with a giant dick popping out. And finally, Manuel is convinced that his babysitter Natalia is stealing stuff and decides to pull off a little stakeout. Manuel thinks he finally catches her in the act but what she's doing is a whole lot better than that!
title: Babysitter Diaries 13
